cdse_client.py — Python CLI Client
====================================

Python 3 command-line client for the CaumeDSE REST API.  Supports encrypted
secret storage, encrypted CSV databases, user/org info, and the audit log.
Runs in one-shot mode (single command per invocation) or in an interactive
REPL with command-line editing.


CONTENTS
========
I.    Prerequisites
II.   Credentials
III.  Quick start
IV.   Command reference
